HEADWORD: Decimetre
<hw>Dec"i*me`tre</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>d⟦eacute⟧cim⟦egrave⟧tre</ets>;
